                        US AIRWAYS VACATIONS

US Airways Vacations is pleased to offer Brussels, Belgium land packages to provide a complete vacation experience.

Vacations include hotel accommodations for up to 59 nights; hotel taxes and service charges; daily breakfast.  A variety of optional features including sightseeing tours; airport/hotel transfers, rental cars and rail passes are available.

EXPERIENCE BELGIUM
------------------
Three nights hotel from:

$107 Tulip Inn Brussels City Centre
$162 Grand Hotel Mercure Royal Crown - Brussels
$237 Sofitel Bruges - Bruges
