Purchase these land packages online at http://www.usairwaysvacations.com/rese.htm  Simply enter your origin and destination cities, departure date, number of adults, children's ages and click "Search For Vacation." Choose "Hotel and Car Vacations for 1-59 nights," confirm your departure date and indicate the number of nights for your vacation. Click "Check Availability" and continue with your choices for hotels and options as the system presents them until you reach the final price. You may then purchase your vacation with a secure credit card transaction.  If you prefer to speak with a reservations agent, call 1-800-352-8747.

Rates shown are per person based on double occupancy for travel 11/28/01 through 12/18/01. Hotel space is limited and may not be available at all hotels on all days. Additional travel dates, hotels and rates are available. Prices are subject to change with or without notice and do not include miscellaneous hotel charges typically paid by the customer directly to the hotel. Substantial restrictions apply for refunds. Other conditions may apply. US Airways' online booking discount is not available on vacation packages.

